  "mūla": {
    "devanāgarī": "न च मां तानि कर्माणि निबध्नन्ति धनंजय | उदासीनवद् आसीनम् असक्तं तेषु कर्मसु",
    "iast": "na ca māṃ tāni karmāṇi nibadhnanti dhanaṃjaya | udāsīnavad āsīnam asaktaṃ teṣu karmasu",
    "chapter_position": "Chapter 9 (Rāja-Vidyā-Rāja-Guhya-Yoga (The Yoga of Royal Knowledge and Royal Mystery)), verse 9",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
  },
